{"tid":1142264,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"超5000名利迷請願：美斯停賽！他打人要追罰","createTime":"2019-05-07T03:18:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T05:42:30.000Z","uid":173952,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"88243f835bde31ba42e84855d2344c9e7a85a0f2","tid":1142264,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"有超過五千名利物浦球迷發起請願活動，要求歐洲足協對美斯（L.Messi）施加停賽處罰。<br />\n<br />\n  在「<a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HAHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=3df96454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a>」網站上，有紅軍球迷發起了請願，訴求和理由如下：「對美斯追加停賽處罰，他很清晰的擊打了法賓奴（Fabinho）的頭部。」<br />\n<br />\n  在首回合巴塞主場對利物浦的一次進攻中，法賓奴阻擋美斯，球證判給巴塞罰球，但利物浦球迷認為，美斯有故意擊打法賓奴頭部的動作。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦球迷：美斯這一下該追加停賽<br />\n<br />\n  在請願書下，很多利物浦球迷留言。一位球迷寫道：「美斯擊打了法賓奴的頭部，卻得到了一個罰球，還攻入了。我認為歐洲足協應該仔細回看這一幕。」<br />\n<br />\n  還有紅軍球迷寫道：「<span style=\"color: red;\">歐洲足協應該回看美斯的舉動。首先是擊打法賓奴，然後偷偷把罰球從原地往前挪了4/5碼。希望歐洲足協有所行動</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n  另有人寫道：「美斯很清晰的擊打了法賓奴的臉，然後他插水在地。」<br />\n<br />\n  （比森霍芬）<br />\n<br />\n應該取消3一0果球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5340d8726bfc3730d9a9e0b726394e439850cf1b","tid":1142264,"uid":71156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2531edd72fe9d931eedaadbe4c56554588342ab1","tid":1142264,"uid":83950,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:32:38.000Z","msg":"咁占士米拿果下直接紅牌先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcbfc0555f904bf15bd0af026195307130da73d4","tid":1142264,"uid":5190,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:32:58.000Z","msg":"利迷對狗眼生係屎忽"},{"pid":"5b8b7d0b35787de17ee224c5bf7c498f8af58393","tid":1142264,"uid":153,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"追返拉莫斯拎返上年冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母拉莫斯"},{"pid":"3733f4d2f953ac9f815b15c0e744c0c6e4fb1d26","tid":1142264,"uid":199590,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/guK0wsP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FguK0wsP.gif&h=93a1153b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9e4575da5392203456fa3c1950d6b446feba602","tid":1142264,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:35:57.000Z","msg":"好肉酸"},{"pid":"b2bac7e33e324b45cf0d50732dc2130150e17ae9","tid":1142264,"uid":63675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:36:57.000Z","msg":"假猁黎嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edd234e06aa9e16e80b408dcd259621857f347ef","tid":1142264,"uid":7435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:37:43.000Z","msg":"連利：呢5千條友都係49000扮利迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3a8ce53da42ab8a6c226e5c17fd0d4ad0c35d5","tid":1142264,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T03:54:55.000Z","msg":"最衰都係美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7d9d9ad3efa590f8b8d575b5e193038c0d82a9","tid":1142264,"uid":62993,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"